------------------------------------------------------------
All tasks runnable from root project
------------------------------------------------------------

Application tasks
-----------------
debug - Runs this program as a JVM application for debugging
run - Runs this project as a JVM application

Build tasks
-----------
androidClasses - Assembles android classes.
assemble - Assembles the outputs of this project.
build - Assembles and tests this project.
buildDependents - Assembles and tests this project and all projects that depend on it.
buildNeeded - Assembles and tests this project and all projects it depends on.
classes - Assembles main classes.
clean - Deletes the build directory.
desktopClasses - Assembles desktop classes.
embeddedClasses - Assembles embedded classes.
iosClasses - Assembles ios classes.
jar - Assembles a jar archive containing the main classes.
testClasses - Assembles test classes.

Build Setup tasks
-----------------
init - Initializes a new Gradle build.
wrapper - Generates Gradle wrapper files.

Distribution tasks
------------------
assembleDist - Assembles the main distributions
distTar - Bundles the project as a distribution.
distZip - Bundles the project as a distribution.
installDist - Installs the project as a distribution as-is.

Documentation tasks
-------------------
javadoc - Generates Javadoc API documentation for the main source code.

Gluon Mobile for Android tasks
------------------------------
android - Generates a debug Android apk containing the JavaFX application.
androidInstall - Launch the application on a connected android device.
androidRelease - Generates a release Android apk containing the JavaFX application.
apkDebug
apkRelease
applyRetrolambda
collectMultiDexComponents
copyClassesForRetrolambda
createMainDexList
dex
mergeAndroidAssets
mergeAndroidResources
mergeClassesIntoJar
processAndroidResourcesDebug
processAndroidResourcesRelease
shrinkMultiDexComponents
validateManifest
validateSigningDebug
validateSigningRelease
writeInputListFile
zipalignDebug
zipalignRelease

Gluon Mobile for Embedded tasks
-------------------------------
copyEmbeddedDependencies
copyJarToEmbeddedPlatform
embeddedJar
runEmbedded - Launch the application on a remote embedded platform.

Gluon Mobile for iOS tasks
--------------------------
createIpa - Generates an iOS ipa containing the JavaFX application.
ios
launchIOSDevice - Launch the application on a connected ios device.
launchIPadSimulator - Launch the application on an iPad simulator.
launchIPhoneSimulator - Launch the application on an iPhone simulator.

Help tasks
----------
buildEnvironment - Displays all buildscript dependencies declared in root project 'OnyxFxMobile'.
components - Displays the components produced by root project 'OnyxFxMobile'. [incubating]
dependencies - Displays all dependencies declared in root project 'OnyxFxMobile'.
dependencyInsight - Displays the insight into a specific dependency in root project 'OnyxFxMobile'.
dependentComponents - Displays the dependent components of components in root project 'OnyxFxMobile'. [incubating]
help - Displays a help message.
model - Displays the configuration model of root project 'OnyxFxMobile'. [incubating]
projects - Displays the sub-projects of root project 'OnyxFxMobile'.
properties - Displays the properties of root project 'OnyxFxMobile'.
tasks - Displays the tasks runnable from root project 'OnyxFxMobile'.

Verification tasks
------------------
check - Runs all checks.
test - Runs the unit tests.

Rules
-----
Pattern: clean<TaskName>: Cleans the output files of a task.
Pattern: build<ConfigurationName>: Assembles the artifacts of a configuration.
Pattern: upload<ConfigurationName>: Assembles and uploads the artifacts belonging to a configuration.

To see all tasks and more detail, run gradlew tasks --all

To see more detail about a task, run gradlew help --task <task>